extends android.os.AsyncTask<java.lang.String,java.lang.Void,java.lang.String>
    This is a class that represents a background thread that will connect to the rest api depending on its task, it will either get the unique ids from the rest api, or obtain all the data and put it into a hash map so that user stats can be displayed Created by Dragos on 10/1/17.
